{"tid":407674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲人你點都唔會忘記到..","createTime":"2017-09-20T15:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T15:30:38.000Z","uid":97165,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6255adc8209f995bc0a92e9babf5c1ed60b7ff","tid":407674,"uid":97165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"就算個陣對你點衰點鬧你...<br />\n到你終於忍唔住同佢分手啦 <br />\n分完手之後都會記翻起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理性話你知再同佢一齊會淨係會比人hurt 同佢唔work <br />\n好啦咁自己就堅持住 <br />\n無論佢點搵你都唔同翻佢一齊啦 <br />\n但過多排都會係咁諗起佢 忍唔住留意佢<br />\n係 一開始都可以好灑脫嘅<br />\n但慢慢真係會發覺自己忘記唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過就算點都好 唔work就係唔work<br />\n講左咁多次會改 你信左 但最後都係唔得 然後一次又一次比人hurt <br />\n咁不如珍惜個個真係會對你好嘅人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999 思緒混亂中 比我9up下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(哈哈我係咁説服自己 叫自己唔好再犯賤落去 btw勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"9502f7c3d92bce58b219de37a0f827b0cde638cd","tid":407674,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"不要再說了"},{"pid":"634049729b7d1e19de4001a41a6dce537b5d564a","tid":407674,"uid":139828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9aac59f92278346d85240e7045004bc422a3164d","tid":407674,"uid":97165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王抒優<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人還是以前更好 回憶夠壞 才吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc7b4d4092426bd09a60a9caa78219c2c50d6b8","tid":407674,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不要再說了</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a484f9e327bc6228fa4722